results/results-baselines/checkpoints/**
!results/results-baselines/checkpoints/naive_sequential_after_T1_LLMail.pt
!results/results-baselines/checkpoints/naive_sequential_after_T2_HackAPrompt.pt
!results/results-baselines/checkpoints/naive_sequential_after_T3_BIPIA.pt

!results/results-ewc+replay/
results/results-ewc+replay/**
!results/results-ewc+replay/checkpoints/
results/results-ewc+replay/checkpoints/**
